snippet.title: Fortnite Ballistic Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Light the fuse in Fortnite’s newest Tactical FPS: Fortnite Ballistic - fn.gg/Ballistic

Welcome to Ballistic, a new first-person Fortnite experience. Launching in early access on December 11 with Ranked and Unranked, Ballistic is an adrenaline-filled, round-based 5v5 competitive game mode where strategy, tactical teamwork, and individual prowess are essential for victory.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fortnite/​
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FortniteGame​
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FortniteGame/​
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@Fortnite
